cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CR, cs.IR 

This paper deals with image generation using GANs and its application to improve the accuracy of license plate recognition. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves deep learning techniques such as DCNN and BRNN, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. The use of GANs for image generation falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also discusses the security aspect of license plate recognition, which could be categorized under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). Finally, the paper involves optimization techniques for mobile and embedded devices, which could be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
